{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dae658b9a9","title":"“农民生活苦的不得了”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"98b795ac69","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"dae658b9a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4413d0090a","name":"洪祖猷"},{"id":"4960c580d5","name":"袁传识"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"ce032a93f2","name":"唐都"},{"id":"ec445d94b0","name":"蔡荣荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3334048e6a","type":"title","text":"“农民生活苦的不得了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"9d9bbecf6c","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院唐都洪祖猷蔡荣荣袁传识","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"0c29e0e07f","type":"paragraph","text":"唐都同意右派分子葛佩琦所谓统购统销搞糟了，并说可以举例来证明。他对右派分子马万钧所谓主要矛盾在农村，也同意的说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"2f9f45f199","type":"paragraph","text":"「实际上农民生活苦的不得了。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"15b7e631a7","type":"paragraph","text":"「统购统销给农民留的粮食太少了，都不够吃，只好吃稀的。」","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"d5b9e3d0ad","type":"paragraph","text":"洪祖猷说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"a506265877","type":"paragraph","text":"「统购统销政策是对的，但下面搞糟了，我回家见到排队买不到肉，机关团体优先权……。」","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"cbc3974d1e","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡荣荣说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"44ccaadfc3","type":"paragraph","text":"「粮食统购统销做得不好，农民吃不饱，而五六年全国粮食没有减产，为什么不让农民吃饭呢？工农生活悬殊太大了。」","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"2ac0329fb9","type":"paragraph","text":"「制定正确的粮食政策是必要的，但是政策的执行中，有些情况掩盖了措施的正确性，使国家遭到损失，政策执行初期，规定每人每月限定购粮十三斤，这种政策是必要的，也是完全失败的。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"5f543557ae","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么说是失败的呢？第一，降低了农民对党的热爱，使党的威信下降，因为粮食是人民生活所绝对必须的，每人每月十三斤粮食，不足以维持最低生活限度，人民不满是自然而然的。第二，影响了五五年的统购工作，造成混乱。第三，在某种程度上扰乱了市场。可以看出统购统销初期的损失比收获来得大。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"e604013dbb","type":"paragraph","text":"袁传识说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"00c4c2d2f8","type":"paragraph","text":"「工农生活悬殊，贫农生活变化不多，特别是江南。」","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"},{"id":"328cd36e2b","type":"paragraph","text":"袁传识说统购统销农民买不到粮食，饿死了他家的八百只鸭子。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9"}],"page":{"id":"b3d6513cb4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dae658b9a9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}